│ data formats are compatible. Monitor synchronization schedules and identify any errors. Cleanse and      │
│ deduplicate data regularly.                                                                              │
│                                                                                                          │
│ 2.  **API Limits:** Monitor API usage to avoid hitting rate limits. Optimize API calls by consolidating  │
